#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Accounting:</b> Automatically log payments, close sessions, and generate "
"tax reports."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Automated Lead Generation:</b> Every submission on your \"Contact Us\" "
"page instantly creates a brand-new opportunity in your <b>CRM App</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Centralize Rewards:</b> Effortlessly build, monitor, and manage your "
"entire ecosystem of loyalty campaigns and promotional programs from one "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Crucial Review:</b> You must review all e-commerce settings to ensure "
"they align with your internal business policies (e.g., when invoices are "
"generated, whether a mandatory customer check-in is required for ordering, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Delivery Methods:</b> Go to <b>Website &gt; Configuration &gt; Delivery "
"Methods</b> to define all available options and their costs."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Direct Redirection:</b> Embed high-converting call-to-action (CTA) "
"buttons that send readers straight to your event registration page."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>E-commerce Category:</b> For easier product retrieval by customers on "
"your online store."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>External Providers:</b> Check if a predefined Odoo connection exists if "
"you work with specific shipping carriers."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>From the CRM app:</b> Track client interactions in real time and use the "
"<b>Sales App</b> to quickly send tailored quotations for B2B leads or custom"
" customer requests."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Generate Membership Barcodes:</b> Link a unique barcode to a customer’s "
"digital or physical membership card for seamless scanning at your Point of "
"Sale (POS)."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>In-Store Pickup (Click &amp; Collect):</b> If you wish to offer this, you"
" must <b>activate the setting</b> within the <b>Website Settings</b> first."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Key Product Settings:</b>"
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Layout Settings:</b> Adjust the visual presentation and layout of "
"products using the <b>website editor</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Logistics &amp; Pricing:</b> Define ticket prices, event times, and "
"capacity limits."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Note:</b> Increased capability leads to higher complexity and more "
"maintenance."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Our Advice:</b> Stick with your current streamlined configuration until "
"you’re fully comfortable. When you're ready to upgrade, try the Inventory "
"module on a duplicated database first to ensure it fits your workflow. 😉"
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Payment Providers &amp; Methods:</b> Go to <b>Website &gt; Configuration "
"&gt; Payment Providers</b> and install <b>all</b> the payment methods and "
"payment providers you plan to offer (e.g., credit card processors, PayPal, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Payroll:</b> Use this feature to handle <b>employee salaries and manage "
"holiday requests</b>."
msgstr ""

#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.homepage
msgid "<b>Photoshoot / June 2021</b>"
msgstr ""

