#. module: art_craft
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:art_craft.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"/>\n"
"            <span class=\"text-o-color-2\" style=\"background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">\n"
"                <font class=\"text-800\">\n"
"                    Tailored specifically for the world of creativity, this Odoo industry package offers a complete solution for arts and crafts stores. It effectively manages a diverse range of inventory with complex variants, ensuring that you can always meet customer demand for specific colors or materials. The system integrates powerful tools for POS and eCommerce, making it easier to run your store efficiently both online and offline. It is the essential tool for combining artistic passion with professional business management.\n"
"                </font>\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""

